OL,6,FShe said: "I firmly believe all
OL,7,Femployers should strive to create safe
OL,8,Fspaces at work where employees can go
OL,9,Fand not only be heard but signposted
OL,10,Fto freedom."
OL,12,FThe event forms part of the Spot the
OL,13,FRed Flags initiative, which was
OL,14,Flaunched in 2022 by the Jersey
OL,15,FSafeguarding Partnership Board (SPB).
OL,17,FSPB manager Cathy Davison said:
OL,18,F"Domestic abuse may happen behind
OL,19,Fclosed doors, but the message of the
OL,20,Fcampaign is that the impact does not
OL,21,Fstay there.
